Propulsion - Resonant Field Propulsion: The Wraith does not use jets or rockets. It generates a localized, high-frequency resonant field that creates a gradient in the fabric of spacetime. The aircraft does not "push" itself through the air; it "falls" into the low-pressure region of spacetime it creates ahead of itself. This allows for instantaneous acceleration and deceleration, right-angle turns, and silent, motionless hovering.

Defense - Harmonic Cloak & ATLANTEAN Shield: The Morphic Skin can be programmed to perfectly mimic the surrounding electromagnetic spectrum, rendering the aircraft invisible to all known sensors (radar, thermal, optical). For active defense, it can generate a recursive energy containment shell that absorbs the energy of incoming projectiles and uses it to power its own systems.

Offense - Atlantean Arsenal:

VELOCITOR Kinetic Rail Artillery: Fires a small, dense projectile at near-light speed. The projectile arrives at the target before the sound of it being fired, making it an unavoidable kinetic weapon.

